Reebok Question Low Green Toe
results.story: The Reebok Question Low ‘Green Toe’ revives a simple two-tone colorway originally released in 2006. Inspired by the storied Boston Celtics franchise, Allen Iverson’s signature shoe is dressed in white leather with a contrasting leather toe cap in Glen Green. The same hue is repeated on the sneaker’s various branding hits, as well as the plastic-reinforced lace loops and translucent rubber outsole. The low-top sits on a lightweight EVA midsole with retro Hexalite cushioning in the heel and forefoot.

Gel Lyte 3 OG 'Earth Day'
results.story: The ASICS Gel Lyte 3 OG ‘Earth Day’ celebrates April 22 with an understated palette and a sustainable build. 20% recycled materials make up the composition of the upper, featuring a blend of leather, suede and textile, the latter made with pre-owned garments and leftover fabric scraps. Additionally, the use of neutral tones mean that less water, inks, and dyes are needed for the coloring process. The split-tongue silhouette rides on a lightweight EVA midsole, supported by a tacky gum rubber outsole.

LeBron 18 Low atmos Viotech
results.story: Created in tandem with the renowned Tokyo-based retailer, the atmos x Nike LeBron 18 Low ‘Viotech’ features a familiar color scheme that takes direct inspiration from a coveted Air Max 1 collaboration from 2003. Like its predecessor, LeBron’s signature low-top features a bold purple Swoosh on a leather and suede build in muted earth tones. A secondary mini-Swoosh in gold embroidery decorates the dark brown suede mudguard. Lightweight cushioning is provided by a large-volume Max Air heel unit with a Nike React midsole, supported by a gum rubber outsole that wraps up the sidewalls.

Jordan 1 Retro High Light Army Rust Shadow Patina
results.story: The Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG 'Patina,' also known as the Jordan 1 'Rust Shadow,' presents an aged take on the iconic sneaker. A black tumbled leather upper is offset with gray nubuck on the heel and collar overlay, further contrasted against a distressed bronze finish on the forefoot overlay, Swoosh and eyestay. Additional details include a woven logo tag surrounded by zigzag stitching atop the black nylon tongue and 'Nike Air' branding in a contrasting pop of mint green. An off-white midsole amplifies the high-top's vintage treatment.

adidas Stan Smith Disney The Little Mermaid
results.story: Dropping as part of ‘The Little Mermaid Collection,’ the Disney x adidas Stan Smith ‘King Triton’ takes inspiration from Ariel’s father and the ruler of the undersea kingdom. The deconstructed upper is built with off-white textile that incorporates recycled Parley Ocean Plastic. A tonal trident graphic adorns the heel tab, while the woven tongue tag features adidas and Disney branding in contrasting pops of Bright Cyan. The interior side features a King Triton graphic and an accompanying quote that reads ‘I consider myself a reasonable merman.’ A translucent rubber cupsole anchors the low-top silhouette.

results.name: adidas Superstar Disney The Little Mermaid
results.story: The Disney x adidas Superstar ‘Ariel’ is taken from ‘The Little Mermaid Collection,’ featuring classic silhouettes in a neutral palette that results from sustainable dye technologies. This pair makes use of an ivory-colored leather upper with scaly-textured three-stripes and an embossed seashell graphic on the heel tab. Dual adidas and Disney branding is stamped on the sockliner and tongue tag, the interior side of which is inscribed with a quote from the titular character that reads: ‘I don’t see how a world that makes such wonderful things could be bad.’

Mallorca 'White Star Sapphire'
results.story: The PUMA Mallorca ‘White Star Sapphire’ brings back a vintage trainer from the brand’s ‘70s archive. The low-top makes use of a white canvas upper with tonal suede detailing on the reinforced toe cap and signature Formstrip. Contrasting color arrives via the sneaker’s various branding elements, including ‘PUMA Mallorca’ stamped in blue on the lateral side panel. Underfoot, PUMA’s Contact No. II rubber outsole provides reliable grip.
